Package: install
Title: Remote R Packages Installation
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi, Hadley Wickham
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <gcsardi@mango-solutions.com>
Description: Download and install R packages stored in 'GitHub',
    'BitBucket' or other 'Git' or 'SVN' repositories.
    This package is a lightweight replacement of 'devtools::install_*()',
    including 'devtools::install_github()'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/mangothecat/install
BugReports: https://github.com/mangothecat/install/issues
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
